    "long_instructions": "#Apply a Consistent Style to Both Web Pages\r\n\r\nYour goal is to style both HTML pages by generating and linking a CSS file based on your chosen mood board.\r\n\r\n:::details [*Don't have your own mood board? You can use one of the following:*]\r\n- [Mood Board 1](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PYPqmPa3DQM7E1hPEwebuHzvzd-zOEqT/view?usp=drive_link)\r\n- [Mood Board 2](https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VcVcmozSAq9OPIhcIQWpNAebk5SOuMbC/view?usp=drive_link)\r\n:::\r\n\r\n:::details [Helpful Steps]\r\n1. Use AI to generate the CSS File\r\n2. Save and Link the Stylesheet\r\n3. Preview Your Work\r\n4. Save as Version 1\r\n:::"
  },
